        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> The ability to cast force or tech powers</em></p>\n<p>You've practiced casting powers more accurately from long range, learning techniques that give you the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When you cast a power that requires you to make an attack roll, the power's range is doubled.</li>\n<li>Your ranged force and tech attacks ignore half cover and three-quarters cover.</li>\n<li>You learn one at-will power that requires an attack roll. Your casting ability for this at-will power depends on the power list you chose from: Wisdom or Charisma (depending on power alignment) for force powers or Intelligence for tech powers.</li>\n</ul>",
